data.description: Contract fell through!  Got through inspection, and appraisal (appraised at 307,000), buyer had too many pets for the HOA and decided to cancel!  Welcome home to your updated, affordable townhome in the Cherry Creek School district!  This property features so many updates, every system and surface has been refinished.  New AC unit, new furnace, newer water heater to start off!  New paint, baseboards, laminate wood flooring, and brand new carpet throughout the property.  The light and bright kitchen has new granite countertops, new glass tile backsplash, and all new cabinets!  The bathroom has a new vanity.  The primary suite boasts a walk in closet.  This property is move in ready!  You get your own 2nd floor covered deck outside your front door, and unit comes with a carport and storage unit for those extras.
